The '''unnamed Nurse''' appears in "[[The One With The Birth]]", played by [[June Gable]].

She first helps deliver [[Lydia]]'s baby and also takes care of [[Joey Tribbiani|Joey]] who breaks down.

Later she helps deliver [[Ben Geller|Ben]], son of [[Carol Willick|Carol]] and [[Ross Geller|Ross]], and adoptive son of [[Susan Bunch|Susan]].

In later seasons June Gable portrayed [[Estelle Leonard]], Joey's agent.
